data.description: This adorable home is ready for its new family.  Featuring 3 bedrooms upstairs, a bonus room in the basement that can easily be used as a 4th bedroom, game room or second family room and an oversized porch that's perfect for entertaining. You'll love the beautifully renovated kitchen and the gorgeous shiplap ceiling. The full, partially finished walk-out basement has a lot of possibilities and could easily be finished to create even more living space. Now let's talk about location, super close to downtown or hit the bypass and be anywhere in Somerset within minutes. This property offers ample parking space, plenty of room for your boat and only a few miles from Burnside Marina, Lees Ford Marina and Slate Branch ramp. This home is perfect for weekend getaways, permanent living or even a VRBO. You really need to see this one.
